blueprint.description:
See book description for necessary mods and settings.

You MUST wait for ALL iron chests AND THE POWER POLES beside them to be placed (can do it manually or just wait for phase#2 to begin) then merge them into two 149x1 long chests.  Be SURE the merge tool shows 298 chests before merging (unless you removed some from the ends) so they don't get broken into multiple lengths.
blueprint.label: Aux Mine
